online\/2013\/01\/24\/hamdulillah-ala-kul-hal\/","url_meta":{"origin":2011,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tahmid: The Prophet praises Allah in every situation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: If the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saw something he liked, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, by whose favor good deeds are accomplished.\u201d If the Prophet\u00a0saw something he disliked, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah in every\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11824,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/shukr-allah-for-his-bounties\/","url_meta":{"origin":2011,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Praise: Thanking Allah for blessings better than receiving","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah does not bestow His bounties upon a servant and he says, 'All praise is due to Allah,' but that what he has given for praise\u00a0is better than what he has taken of bounties.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/umar-on-hamd-how-are-you-all-praise-is-due-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2011,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Hamd: How are you? All praise is 